[2026-07-02T12:07:39.814Z] [INFO] [stdout] **Detail:** The entry animation `chat-popup-in` lacks `animation-fill-mode: backwards`. The element's pre-animation state (default `opacity: 1`, `transform: none`) can flash before the animation applies the `from` keyframe (`opacity: 0`, `translateY(16px) scale(0.96)`). On some browsers this produces a visible flash of the fully-opaque popup before it fades in.
[2026-07-02T12:07:39.814Z] [INFO] [stdout] **Recommendation:** Change to `chat-popup-in ${duration}ms ease-out backwards`.
